description:
This program is one in a series of acclaimed animated films presented by the BBC. Religions of the World / Our World Faith is a collection of ten 15-minute shorts for children, educating them on the diversity of the major world religions. Included are stories about Christianity, Judaism, Buddhism, Sikhism, Sufism, Islam, Hinduism, and Confucianism.
Narrators include Bert Reo Anderson and Ben Kingsley

